A: King Tormax, Vindicator, Velkethor<br>
<br>
Q: What Dragons can I hit with Dragon Bane?<br>
A: Warders in Sleepers Tomb, Yelinak, Tov dragons with Lord or Lady in their name. No Kunark Dragons.<br>
<br>
Q: Is the aggro created by Banespells the same as for other DDspells?<br>
A: Dragonbane: Seems not, way less. Giantbane: Probably, maybe even more.<br>
<br>
Q: Do I need Meleerange for Banes?<br>
A: No. Line of Sight is all you need.<br>
<br>
<br>
